{"tid":218181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"節目表曝光】奇妙電視開台狂播財經","createTime":"2017-04-26T10:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T12:47:53.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86c0e9631976d73f558ae594e6d93a9126256e8b","tid":218181,"uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"奇妙電視在今年5月14日正式啟播。近期有線新主，由純官領軍的永升話要主力發展財經新聞，結果奇妙電視由早上6時至下午12時半，再由下午1時至5時半都在播財經節目，十分誇張！<br />\n<br />\n奇妙電視節目表顯示，一早就播3小時《創富早餐》，然後有《交易所直播室》、《窩輪攻略》等財經節目。你以為已播完財經？不，小休半小時後，下午1時就有《開市埋位》，接著都是財經節目包括《外匯先機》、《商品有價》等。直到下午5時半，才完結財經環節！早晨同午間新聞呢？是不見蹤影的...."},{"pid":"b3d838e1c579b79d0cadb238d4343b48dd50490d","tid":218181,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170426/large/1493195224_10e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493195224_10e6.png&h=09f95143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a5fd377062e91e07e06de7004b3a327e99c93c","tid":218181,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"魚樂無窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23761b9c08278643be527876dec311ef5fabe495","tid":218181,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e889c85a1d7e1cfab4852b38241fc2f13cf1c72f","tid":218181,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"Talk show 低成本 又可以有sponsor"},{"pid":"b0160e415afedd783db5c99a171adb274fee6d55","tid":218181,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"有線中國組呢？"},{"pid":"63259d1185cc22663dac2581092988f490bc910d","tid":218181,"uid":14009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"亞洲電視舊老細<br />\n<br />\n零期望"},{"pid":"1f7cc